```http
### Health Check (Public)
GET http://localhost:5257/api/health

### Register New User
POST http://localhost:5257/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### Login (Demo User)
POST http://localhost:5257/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@ballastlane.com",
  "password": "Pa$$w0rd!"
}

### List My Tasks (Replace TOKEN with value from login response)
GET http://localhost:5257/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGci...

### Create Task
POST http://localhost:5257/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGci...

{
  "title": "New Interview Task",
  "description": "Prepare for Ballastlane",
  "dueDate": "2026-05-30T00:00:00Z"
}

### Update Task
PUT http://localhost:5257/api/tasks/{TASK_ID}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGci...

{
  "title": "Updated Task",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "status": "InProgress",
  "dueDate": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z"
}

### Delete Task
DELETE http://localhost:5257/api/tasks/{TASK_ID}
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGci...